en_866107_0	Major General R.M.P.J Rathnayaka assumed office as 9th General Officer Commanding (GOC) of the 68 Division on Monday (6) at his office in Kombavil, Mullaittivu.
en_866107_1	A Guard Turnout plus a parade saluted the new GOC before he signed an official document to symbolize the acceptance of the new appointment.
en_866107_2	Afterwards, Major General Rathnayake planted a sandalwood sapling in the premises and joined refreshments.
en_866107_3	A few minutes later, he addressed the troops and explained his vision.
en_866107_4	Brigade Commanders of under command Brigades, staff officers of the Division, Commanding Officers were present at the venue.
